By rhaamo <rhaamo@sigpipe.me>

Compile it from sources with patchs from https://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=54732
Or use
	mkdir fvwm-build ; cd fvwm-build ; ./build-fvwm2.sh


git clone git://github.com/rhaamo/fvwm2.git ~/.fvwm2
cd ~/.fvwm2
cd thumb
make -f GNUMakefile
OR
gmake
cp thumb ../scripts/

Enjoy!
